      "span_text": "Similarly, electric isolation may not be necessary in the interconnection of HVDC systems, and a novel inductor-capacitor-inductor (LCL) type dc/dc converter presented in is able to achieve high voltage stepping ratio without the need of ac transformer, but the two conversion stages are still required."
